  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To Evaluate combined effect of vitrectomy and bevacizumab to stabilize retinal thickness and
      visual acuity in patients with diffuse diabetic macular edema and their relation to renal
      disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
